      SalaryUpdateLog findByInstructorAndDate​(Long instructorId, LocalDate createdDate)
      Finds salary update log by the given instructor id and created date in the format of LocalDate. Since the RequestTime is persisted as Instant type, it should be converted.
      Parameters:
      instructorId - Id of the instructor
      createdDate - request time
      Returns:
      the log object
